  m_text: "That is all you need to know. \nIt takes a bit of practice so be patient\n\nRemember:\n1.
    You need to keep the circle steady, if you move away from the object it will
    cancel the selection\n2. If it still isn't working. try looking away from the
    object so the circle changes to a dot then try again\n\nIf you suffer from motion
    sickness we suggest you avoid the adrenaline films!\n\nIf you have any medical
    conditions please consult with your doctor before using Virtual Reality\n\nHave
    fun and explore"
